[font_size=48]Collaborators[/font_size]
[font_size=32]Henry Wauzivuff[/font_size]
[font_size=24]Main Developer[/font_size]
[img=80]res:///assets/Artworks/HenryWauzivuff Icon.jpg[/img]
Developer & programmer. Custom assets too.

[font_size=32]Ferdowski[/font_size]
[font_size=24]Rules of Hokm[/font_size]
[img=80]res:///assets/Artworks/Ferdowski Icon.png[/img]
All of this is possible because FerdowSki (my man) who happened to teach me this game in late 2025

[font_size=32]Art & Assets[/font_size]
Henry Wauzivuff - Custom Assets
Kenney.nl - [url=https://kenney.nl/assets/playing-cards-pack]Playing Cards Pack[/url]
Noobytube - [url=https://godotshaders.com/shader/balatro-paint-mix/]Balatro Paint Mix (CC0)[/url]

[font_size=24]Music & SFX[/font_size]
Nasser Abdollahi - [url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NsyFWR9IYHQ]Ziyafat[/url]
Robin Alciatore & Erik Satie - [url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Erik_Satie_-_gymnopedies_-_la_1_ere._lent_et_douloureux.ogg]Gymnopédies - No. 1 lent et douloureux[/url]
